  "texts": [
    "Communication Cost Discussion.",
    "Compared to traditional FedSeqRec, the primary additional communication cost comes from calling the LLM services.",
    "Specifically, for the central server, the extra cost involves sending the textual information V 𝑡𝑥 to the LLM server, but this is a one-time expense at the beginning of the training process.",
    "For the clients, the additional cost comes from transmitting the noisy sequence S, which is just a sequence of numbers.",
    "Given the sparse nature of interaction data, this communication cost is minimal."
  ],
